profile:
Can Do More Painting - Renovation and Design is your professional Multi-Year Award Winning Painting & Renovation company with full interior, exterior, residential, and commercial capabilities.  This includes all painting and stain finishes with full spraying capabilities. We do it all... stain and/or lacquer, custom new builds, renovations, and repainting. 

We have a state-of-the-art REFINISHING & SPRAY SHOP to handle all your cabinet refinishing and project needs. As our name states we DO more than just painting so we can take care of your renovation needs as well (flooring, tile, countertops, electrical, plumbing, drywall, carpentry, and much more)

We have 2 websites to showcase our work and discuss our capabilities and in-depth processes:
---INTERIOR AND EXTERIOR PAINTING WEBSITE: www.candomorepainting.com
---CABINET REFINISHING AND RENOVATIONS WEBSITE: www.cabinetpaintingandrefinishingcalgary.com


Choosing the right contractor is a big decision and we know it so it may please you to know that:
- We are Baeumler Approved by HGTV Canada’s Handyman Host, Bryan Baeumler
- A+ rating with BBB and no claims plus more reviews than any other painter in Canada! 
- On HomeStars we have a 10 out of 10-star rating and won the BEST OF 2018 - 2022 AWARD! 
- On Houzz, we also carry a full 5 star rating and won the BEST OF 2018 - 2022 AWARD for Customer Satisfaction! 
- On Google, YellowPages.ca, and Yelp, we have a 5 out of 5-star rating with positive reviews to read.


   We hope all this gives you the peace of mind you deserve when choosing us for your project. If you would like contact information of some of our previous clients so you can speak to them directly, please let us know.


   ---   CHECK OUT THE GALLERY SECTION FOR LOTS OF PROJECT PHOTOS   ---
products: *Large or small we do it all! We provide products and labour for: Residential Home Owners, Custom Home Builders, Remodeling Contractors, Commercial Builders, Property Management Companies, Town House Communities, Condominium Owners, Commercial Property Owners, Real Estate Developers, Apartment Owners, And anyone else that is looking to hire a trusted contractor!
services:
*Can Do More Painting is your one source for all your COMPLETE painting and renovation needs – interior or exterior.

*We have a state-of-the-art REFINISHING & SPRAY SHOP to handle all your cabinet refinishing and project needs.

*On your project, we maintain a clean working space and leave the work space clean daily! We believe our customers appreciate the Can Do More difference and invite you to discover it for yourself. 


*Our price will provide a premium, high-quality products, an experienced, top-notch team, and a detailed renovation process that will provide awesome results. You can feel protected knowing that we are licenced in Calgary (plus surrounding areas) and though the Alberta Government plus carry $5 million in liability insurance. We are also bonded and carry WCB insurance.
brands:
*We use Benjamin Moore, Cloverdale, and Sherwin Williams premium paint on our interior and exterior projects. Plus we ensure all our trades use industry standard or premium products - never cutting corners on quality. 

*All brands have low end and top quality products. We believe in using the best products available for each brand.

*Our quality paint will provide: Colour Lock technology for exceptional colour, Mildew resistance, Colours don't rub off when cleaning, Seamless touch-ups, Long-lasting, fresh look, and Zero VOCs
specialities:
*RENOVATIONS and PAINTING... INTERIOR & EXTERIOR projects require different specialties. 

*For your RENOVATION, we specialize in cabinets, countertops, tile, floor, plumbing and kitchen and bath fixtures, electrical and light fixtures, framing, drywall, texturing, plus millwork and finishing. Kitchen, bath, and basement renovations are our most common projects.

*In your INTERIOR we specialize in drywall repair, hard to access areas, total home transformation, trim, doors, walls, kitchen cabinets, and ceiling painting. Spray finishing and rolling. 

*We have a state-of-the-art REFINISHING & SPRAY SHOP to handle all your cabinet refinishing and project needs

*On your EXTERIOR we specialize in hard to access areas, painting on stucco, wood siding, fascia, soffit, eves, downspouts, decks, and fences.

profile:
Why Choose Mill Creek Painters?

At Mill Creek Painters, we are proud to say that we are one of the best Residential and Commercial Painting Contractors in Edmonton and in Calgary. With over 25 years experience, we promise our clients to provide the highest quality painting and contracting services at highly competitive rates. We guarantee by the end of the project you will have an environment as unique as you!

To make this possible we offer to all clients:
Outstanding Customer Service: Our staff are available to answer any and all of your questions. Your inquiries will be responded quickly, and regardless of your schedule!

Free In-Home Colour Consultations: House & Condo Painters specially provide free colour consultation before starting the job. We will give you our professional opinion on the colour and finish combinations that will make your home as you dream!

We Only Use High-Quality Paint: We only use well-known and trusted products to deliver the best results for your home. Often working with brands such as Benjamin Moore, Sherwin Williams, Cloverdale, we will never use paint below the "Super" grade. This will ensure you have a high-quality paint job that is washable and durable for years to come. All left-over paint is left with you for future projects.

Experienced Professionals: At Mill Creek Painters we only hire professional, skilled painters for all of our projects. This helps us to ensure that the work we provide is of the highest quality and completed within the shortest amount of time.

profile:
Neighbourhood Painters is a well established local company since 2003 located in Calgary, We have been restoring home, apartment, condo, store, office or commercial building. All our painters are experienced to do diverse projects. They have completed the required safety & fall protection courses. We are bonded and have a clean appearance. Our employees are certified and offer a friendly professional service.We offer a high quality paint job delivered on time and on budget.

****

Communication with our customers is important and we want you to be satisfied with every aspect of the project. We are here to help you with your painting needs, whether it is a small or big project. We are proud of our work and the relationships we build with our clients. After 10 years, we continue to maintain a  beautiful resort in Priddis. We also paint commercial and residential properties all over Calgary and the surrounding areas. We always stand behind our work and customer satisfaction is our #1 priority.

****

Over the years we have tested many different products and ways to accomplish a variety of projects. We have grown a lot over the years continuing to grow our team and clientele. We leave your home like we've never been there and the only thing that will have changed is the paint job! We offer only the best, done right on time !

****

Business Owner: Andy Poirier:

****

A little bit about me and my painting career
I started my career with my dad, who is a professional painter, at the age of 15. He slowly taught me everything he knew about painting. I’ve never seen painting as a job but more as a passion. In post-secondary, I studied architecture for a year, then soon realize I wanted to return to my career as a painter. My brief foray into architecture was not wasted time, as I have now a valuable skill in understanding how to read drawing plans. 

****

Since then I have successfully completed and received my diploma in Business. During that time, I worked for a pine shop for two years. It was here that I learned the art of staining and varnishing floors, furniture, baseboards, and trim.

****

At the age of 20, I moved to Alberta from Quebec and have spent the last five years establishing myself in Calgary. I work for Ryan, the previous owner of this company for five years and for the last two years I was his project manager. For me, Alberta life is fantastic. I get to enjoy the mountains and all the outdoors activities it holds. I love to go hiking, camping, and snowboarding.

****

I am thrilled to say that I am now the new owner of Neighbourhood Painters and I can’t wait to meet you and help you with any and all your painting needs.

profile:
At Five Star Painting, we understand the importance of color. From a fresh exterior paint job that improves the curb appeal of your home or business, to interior paint that brings style and feeling to your daily life, paint can make all the difference. Don’t put off that painting project any longer, call the professionals at Five Star Painting and start enjoying your freshly painted home sooner than later.
If you are ready to get started on your painting project, contact Five Star Painting to schedule your free estimate. Our convenient online calendar allows you to choose the date and time that works with your schedule. Our team will show up at the scheduled time and provide you with an exact price estimate for the job you have in mind. Whether it be an interior project involving painting and wallpaper removal or an exterior project such as pressure cleaning or deck restoration, estimates are always free and provided at no obligation.
